## Build and preview locally

1. **Install Quarto** (v1.4 or newer): <https://quarto.org/docs/get-started/>.
   No other toolchain is required — the quiz uses only Quarto's built-in
   Observable JS support, so there is no `npm install` step.

2. **Preview with live reload** from the project root:

   ```bash
   quarto preview
   ```

   This opens the site in your browser and reloads on save. Because the quiz
   reads the CSV at runtime, editing `data/questions.csv` and refreshing shows
   your changes immediately.

3. **Render a production build** into `_site/`:

   ```bash
   quarto render
   ```

   The `_site/` directory is a self-contained static site you can host anywhere.

